/app/generated/prisma

# Local SQLite database — contains customer/invoice data + binary CSVs/PDFs
# stored as `source_bytes` and ContractSource.bytes. Re-derivable from the
# original files; not source-of-truth. Excluded for both size (~130 MB) and
# confidentiality.
dev.db
dev.db-journal
dev.db.backup-*
